**Summary:** This documentation explains three methods for creating cohorts in Amplitude: using Microscope to create static or behavioral cohorts from data points, importing static cohorts from CSV files with user/Amplitude IDs, and creating inline behavioral cohorts with interval filtering directly within the Segmentation module (excluding Compass charts).

